20:49.231 --> 20:51.474
So, Blythe dumped me for a guy

20:51.476 --> 20:53.642
she says is a better
spiritual match for her.

20:53.644 --> 20:56.645
Also, he's super rich
and can eat corn.

20:56.647 --> 20:59.072
He's taking Calvin to Africa
to study animals

20:59.074 --> 21:01.092
in their natural habitat.

21:01.094 --> 21:03.486
I'll miss that little scamp,
but you know,

21:03.488 --> 21:06.931
I'm glad you and I
are finally communicating.

21:06.933 --> 21:10.493
I love you, son.
Anyway, call me back.

21:10.495 --> 21:13.271
-(phone chimes)
-Your dad left you
another message.

21:13.273 --> 21:15.690
Eh, it's probably
just a butt-dial.

21:28.679 --> 21:29.662
Shh!
